About Us Your Florida Getaway Fisherman’s Cove is the premiere RV destination in central Florida. Our proximity to Disney, Daytona, and Tampa makes us the convenient choice for adventure travelers and retirees. When you stay with us, you are joining our family. Everything we do, we do it to the highest standard, because we—just like you—love being active, socializing, pleasure boating, exploring the outdoors, and more. Our marina, golf course, spacious concrete pads, vast list of amenities, and central location sets us a notch above the rest. View Property Map Resort Amenities Nine-hole golf course Full-service marina Heated swimming pool Hot tub Full-scale fitness center Boat ramp Resort wide Wi-Fi On-site laundry facility Extra bathrooms and showers Boat wet slips High and dry boat storage Paved and lighted streets On-site post office Shuffleboard courts Boat store Planned activities Play Outside Nine-Hole Golf Course Experience the natural beauty of Lake Harris as your ball soars through the air on our challenging nine-hole golf course featuring extraordinary views of Lake Harris. Break A Sweat Full-Scale Fitness Center Maintain your health in our full-scale fitness center featuring exercise equipment for every age. Challenge yourself to be more active this year. Bring Fido Pet-Friendly We can’t wait to welcome you and your furry friends. All family members are welcome at our resort, as long as they are friendly, like their parents.
